      "content": "oh sorry, i didnt mean anything rude lol. i'm just trying to understand the anthropological framework for my paper. i'm specifically looking at how different cultures reached different stages of development. like, in most textbooks, there's a distinction between how western european societies structured their laws vs how indigenous or tribal groups in africa or the americas did things. can you help me clarify those academic distinctions?",
